The paper discusses an algorithm that performs dimensionality reduction on high dimensional input signals and applies it to a setting inspired by reinforcement learning to control an agent in an environment. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), systems and control (cs.SY), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and robotics (cs.RO).
